1. Rotations of 90, 180 and 270 degrees.
2. Vertical and Horizontal flips
3. Rotation and flipping (avoided for images rotated by 180 degrees)

4. Padded images were given the above (1-3) augmentations

5. Images greater than 350 dimension were cropped by 50 pixels on either side (top, bottom left and right) and augmented by (1-3)
6. Images greater than 1000 dimension were cropped by 100 pixels on either side (top, bottom left and right) and augmented by (1-3)
